Getting Sick

Sleeps left in Australia: 2

Went out to lunch with my mum and my little sister yesterday... went up
to the Rue de Paris for some antipasto and pasta - along with too much
coffee and way to much left over chocolate from easter :)

Today I spent the day wandering around Toowong getting last minute
things sorted, meant to go over Liam's place but totally forgot - sorry
dude! Got my tax return lodged - after the $100 fee they charge I'll
still be getting a bit of cash back so that's (obviously) better than
nothing.

Tried cancelling my comm bank credit card and found out it's a lot
harder than you'd think. They are still processing charges from 9 days
ago and until they finish processing them they can't give me a payout
fee which means I can't finalise the card.... GRRR!!!! If it isn't
sorted by tomorrow I'll crack the shits and let them have it heh :)

Going to go have 2 for 1 dinners at the Caxton with Joel, Sam, Sarah and Gill now.

Jamie out
